<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= category.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + category.slice(1) %> Machines</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

    <div class="p-5">
        <h2 class="display-6 text-center"><%= category.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + category.slice(1) %> Machines</h2>
        <p class="text-center"><%= category.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + category.slice(1) %> workouts are an essential part of fitness. Shop the range of <%= category %> machines at GymEquipment.co.uk.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container text-center row">
        <div class="col-4 px-5">
            <h2 class="pb-5">Shopping Options</h2>
            <h3>Price</h3>
            <form id="filterForm">
                <div class="container border-top pt-5 mb-5">
                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                        <span class="input-group-text">Min Price</span>
                        <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="£0" id="minPrice" name="minPrice">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                        <span class="input-group-text">Max Price</span>
                        <input type="number" class="form-control" placeholder="£0" id="maxPrice" name="maxPrice">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3>Manufacturer</h3>
                <div class="container ps-2 pt-5 ms-2 border-top">
                        <% manufacturer_list.forEach(manufacturer => { %>
                            <div class="input-group">
                                    <input class="form-check-input mt-2" style="border: 1px solid black" type="checkbox" value="<%= manufacturer %>" name="manufacturer" id="<%= manufacturer %>">
                                <label class="lead ms-3 " for="<%= manufacturer %>"><%= manufacturer %></label>
                            </div>
                        <% }) %>
                </div>
                <input type="hidden" id="page" name="page" value="1">
                <button type="submit" class="btn text-white container-fluid mt-5" style="background-color: var(--color1);">Filter</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center col-8">
            <% if (products.length > 0) { %>
                <div class="row row-cols-3 row-gap-3">
                    <% products.forEach(product => { %>
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="card text-center card-hover">
                                <img src="images/equipment_images/<%= product.name %>.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="equipment-image">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="card-title" style="height: 80px;"><%= product.name %></h5>
                                    <h4 class="card-text mb-3">£<%= product.price %></h4>
                                    <button class="btn text-white" style="background-color: var(--color1);">More info</button>
                                    <button class="btn text-white" style="background-color: var(--color2);">Buy Now</button>
                                </div>    
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 text-start">
                    <label for="page">Page:</label>
                    <% for (let i = 1; i <= totalPages; i++) { %>
                        <button class="btn btn-sm text-white" style="background-color: var(--color2);" onclick="changePage(i)"><%= i %></button>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="mt-5 mx-auto" style="width: 80%;">

    <div class="container-fluid text-center p-5">
        <p class="lead mx-5">
            If you want to help build your fitness and protect yourself against heart disease, then cardio is the way to go. Here, you'll find a wide selection of gym cardio machines designed for a wide range of cardio workouts, from walking and running to cycling and rowing.

            Exercise bikes are perhaps the most popular piece of cardio equipment. These offer low impact workouts that are great for joints. You might also be interested in our selection of spin bikes, perfect for spinning classes. Along with the exercise bike, treadmills are the most used gym equipment in any gym or studio, allowing you to run or walk from the comfort of a dry and warm environment.

            Also in our collection is the rowing machine, which offers a full body workout, including upper body conditioning. Finally, our cardio gym equipment also includes cross trainers and steppers, which offer a low impact, medium- to high-intensity workout that's perfect for beginners. Looking for something more intense? Take a look at our collection of HIIT machines, which includes HIIT Skier machines and more.

            Cardio machines form the foundation of any good gym space, so shop the collection at GymEquipment.co.uk to get started. Why not enquire about our expert gym room design service? We'll do everything from the initial design to choosing the equipment and fitting out your space, so you can create the perfect fitness studio for your needs.
        </p>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
